{{Infobox Figure Skating Competition | title= 1987 Prague Skate | image= | imagesize= | caption= | comptype= | startdate= 5 November | enddate= 8 November 1987 | skatingseason= | location= [[Prague]] | host= | venue= | prizemoney= | championmen= {{flagathlete|[[Petr Barna]]|TCH}} | championladies= {{flagathlete|[[Lotta Falkenbäck]]|SWE}} | championpairs= {{flagathlete|[[Mandy Wötzel]] / [[Axel Rauschenbach]]|GDR}} | championdance= {{flagathlete|[[Renee Rocca]] / [[James Yorke (figure skater)|James Yorke]]|USA}} | previouscomp= [[1986 Prague Skate]] | nextcomp= [[1988 Prague Skate]] | previousgp= | nextgp= }}
The '''1987 [[Prague Skate]]''' was held November 1987. Medals were awarded in the disciplines of [[single skating|men's singles, ladies' singles]] and [[pair skating]].
